Core Commands.name: Ping
Core Commands.description: Returns the ping of the bot to the Discord server

Core Commands.name: Info
Core Commands.description: Returns information about the Discord bot

Core Commands.name: Help
Core Commands.description: Messages user with a list of commands and help documentation

Launch Commands.name: Next Launch
Launch Commands.description: Returns the information for the next planned launch from Earth

Launch Commands.name: List Launches
Launch Commands.description: Returns the information for a number of planned launches from Earth

Launch Commands.name: Add Countdown Channel
Launch Commands.description: Adds countdown alerts to the channel the command was ran in

Launch Commands.name: Remove Countdown Channel
Launch Commands.description: Removes countdown alerts to the channel the command was ran in

Reddit Commands.name: Add SubReddit
Reddit Commands.description: Adds the given subreddit read outs to the channel the command was ran in

Reddit Commands.name: Remove Subreddit
Reddit Commands.description: Removes the given subreddit read outs to the channel the command was ran in

Twitter Commands.name: Add Twitter
Twitter Commands.description: Adds the given twitter user read outs to the channel the command was ran in

Twitter Commands.name: Remove Twitter
Twitter Commands.description: Removes the given twitter user read outs to the channel the command was ran in
